{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_018uXdV5a71mgjUbookWjYaE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Both trace IDs in the access log match the trace IDs received by the collector. All success criteria are met.\n\nHere's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Resources created:**\n- `otel` namespace with `otel-collector` deployment + service (OTLP gRPC on port 4317)\n- `demo/otel-echo` deployment + service (echo backend on port 5678)\n- `demo/otel-ingress` — Ingress routing `otel.example.com` → `otel-echo:5678`\n\n**ConfigMap `ingress-nginx-controller` patched with:**\n- `enable-opentelemetry: \"true\"` — loads `otel_ngx_module.so` and instruments all requests\n- `otlp-collector-host: otel-collector.otel.svc` — the correct key (not `opentelemetry-collector-host`)\n- `otlp-collector-port: \"4317\"`\n- `otel-sampler: AlwaysOn` — 100% sampling\n- `otel-sampler-parent-based: \"false\"` — don't defer to parent's sampling decision\n- `log-format-upstream` — custom format including `otel_trace_id=$opentelemetry_trace_id otel_span_id=$opentelemetry_span_id`\n\n**Key finding:** The ingress-nginx v1.14.1 configmap key for the collector host is `otlp-collector-host`, not `opentelemetry-collector-host` — the binary template reveals `json:\"otlp-collector-host\"`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":391,"cache_read_input_tokens":53007,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":391},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bd487f94-0c3d-45b2-be20-9528aacb64d1","uuid":"9454fb69-2625-4c73-a8f2-b6e1069de61e","request_id":"req_011Cc6j1gfLE8CjhfWugbFYX"}
